New Records: Kyle Schwarber set an MLB record with his 14th leadoff homer of the season
Key Match Events: Trea Turner hit two, two-run homers
Cal Stevenson hit a tiebreaking two-run double in the eighth inning
Bryce Harper had three doubles in a game for the third time in his career
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Phillies (87-58) moved 29 games over.500, matching a season high
Others: Kyle Schwarber left the game in the fourth inning due to left elbow discomfort
